The paper deals with the application of machine learning algorithms to financial data, specifically for the purpose of predicting price changes. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of tensor-based learning algorithms is a key aspect of the paper, which could also place it in the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also involves the analysis of large datasets, which could place it in the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
